'''-{zh:薩辛·坦都卡;zh-hans:薩辛·坦都卡;zh-tw:薩辛·坦都卡;zh-hk:沙奇·德魯卡;}-'''（[[马拉地语|马拉地语]]：सचिन रमेश तेंडुलकर，[[英语|英语]]：Sachin Tendulkar，{{bd|1973年|4月24日}}），[[印度|印度]][[板球|板球]]运动员，被认为是板球历史上最伟大的击球手之一。他保持着[[板球对抗赛|板球对抗赛]]（Test cricket）和[[单日国际板球赛|单日国际板球赛]]（ODI，One Day International cricket）的最高[[跑_(板球)|跑位]]得分纪录，且都曾在一局比赛中完成过[[100跑|100跑]]。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/StoryPage/StoryPage.aspx?id=31d055a3-de0d-4969-93bf-82b186a50fc0&ParentID=d9bbcde5-db34-4afc-87e6-e4cca6aa5033&MatchID1=4586&TeamID1=1&TeamID2=8&MatchType1=1&SeriesID1=1151&MatchID2=4588&TeamID3=3&TeamID4=5&MatchType2=1&SeriesID2=1152&PrimaryID=4586&Headline=Tendulkar+is+Warne's+greatest | title=Tendulkar is Shane Warne's Greatest | publisher=[[印度斯坦时报|印度斯坦时报]] | accessdate=2008-06-01 | archive-date=2012-12-09 | archive-url=https://archive.today/20121209061542/http://www.hindustantimes.com/StoryPage/StoryPage.aspx?id=31d055a3-de0d-4969-93bf-82b186a50fc0&ParentID=d9bbcde5-db34-4afc-87e6-e4cca6aa5033&MatchID1=4586&TeamID1=1&TeamID2=8&MatchType1=1&SeriesID1=1151&MatchID2=4588&TeamID3=3&TeamID4=5&MatchType2=1&SeriesID2=1152&PrimaryID=4586&Headline=Tendulkar+is+Warne's+greatest | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.india-today.com/itoday/04051998/sport.html | title=The Best Cricketer | publisher=[[今日印度|今日印度]] | accessdate=2008-06-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080608084651/http://www.india-today.com/itoday/04051998/sport.html | archive-date=2008-06-08 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.dawn.com/2004/03/17/spt2.htm | publisher=[[Dawn_(newspaper)|Dawn]] | title=Tendulkar is greatest, says Pakistan's Captain Inzamam | accessdate=2008-06-01 | archive-date=2008-05-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080527163533/http://www.dawn.com/2004/03/17/spt2.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref> 他也是ODI历史上唯一一个曾得到过200跑的击球手。<ref>[http://stats.cricinfo.com/ci/content/current/records/216972.html Auto-updated statistics: One-Day Internationals Batting records – Most runs in an innings] {{Wayback|url=http://stats.cricinfo.com/ci/content/current/records/216972.html |date=20100420145447 }}Cricinfo</ref>2002年《维斯登板球年鉴》（Wisden Cricketers' Almanack）评出的史上最伟大击球手中他仅次于[[唐纳德·布莱德曼|唐纳德·布莱德曼]]排名第二，而在ODI史上最伟大击球手评选中他也仅次于[[维维安·理查兹|维维安·理查兹]]（Viv Richards）。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rediff.com/cricket/2002/dec/13wisden.htm |title=Tendulkar second-best ever: Wisden |publisher=Rediff.com |date= |accessdate=2008-11-27 |archive-date=2009-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090123042213/http://www.rediff.com/cricket/2002/dec/13wisden.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>2007年9月，[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]传奇投手[[谢恩·沃恩|谢恩·沃恩]]（Shane Warne）认为德鲁卡是曾和他一起比赛过的最伟大的球手。<ref name="timesonline1">{{cite news |url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/columnists/shane_warne/article2364258.ece |title=Shane Warne's 50 greatest cricketers |publisher=[[泰晤士报|泰晤士报]] |accessdate=2008-06-01 |archive-date=2008-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080513094455/http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/columnists/shane_warne/article2364258.ece |dead-url=no }}</ref>他还是与他同代的球手中唯一一个入选“布莱德曼11人梦之队”<ref>{{cite news |author=CBC Sports |url=http://www.cbc.ca/sports/story/2001/08/13/bradman010813.html |title=Late Bradman rates top 11 cricketers |publisher=Cbc.ca |date= |accessdate=2008-11-27 |archive-date=2008-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081219151957/http://www.cbc.ca/sports/story/2001/08/13/bradman010813.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>的。他有些时候被称作“小大师”（Little Master）或“爆破大师”（Master Blaster）。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.hindu.com/2004/12/12/stories/2004121202031900.htm | title=Article on Sachin's 34th Century | publisher=[[印度报|印度报]] | accessdate=2008-06-01 | archive-date=2008-05-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080503185851/http://www.hindu.com/2004/12/12/stories/2004121202031900.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/cricket/6462199.stm| title=Tendulkar achieves superhero status| publisher=BBC News| accessdate=2008-06-01| date=2007-03-17| archive-date=2008-09-18| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080918040553/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/cricket/6462199.stm| dead-url=no}}</ref>
